rows.label: tlk502108_msg0002
rows.name:
You can tell good wood when
you see it, young lady?

rows.label: tlk502108_msg0003
rows.name:
Yes, I can! I have a special
affinity with trees and plants.

rows.label: tlk502108_msg0005
rows.name:
Yeah, that's right. It's used
to make musical instruments.

rows.label: tlk502108_msg0006
rows.name:
They're one of Liberalitas's
famous exports.

rows.label: tlk502108_msg0007
rows.name: I'm sure it makes them sound lovely...

rows.label: tlk502108_msg0008
rows.name:
It sure does. Nothing
quite like it, is there?

rows.label: tlk502108_msg0011
rows.name:
Why don't you take a few
pieces with you, young lady?

rows.label: tlk502108_msg0013
rows.name:
Yeah. There's more here than you
could count in a lifetime. It
wouldn't hurt if you took a few.

rows.label: tlk502108_msg0014
rows.name:
Most of the youngsters round here are only
interested in salvaging - it's rare to see
anyone show an interest in lumber.

rows.label: tlk502108_msg0015
rows.name:
It really cheers me up to
speak to a girl like you.

rows.label: tlk502108_msg0022
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Think ] Perhaps my charm failed me this time.
